; Regression test for issue #1129: Ignores meta tags with space (BZ#1129)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1129
;
; Meta tags (metadata comments) with spaces in the tag name are ignored.
; e.g., "; Some Tag: value" should create tag "Some Tag" with value "value",
; but ledger currently ignores it entirely.

2024/01/01 Test transaction
    ; SomeTag: found
    ; Some Tag: should-also-be-found
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; Bug: tag("Some Tag") should return "should-also-be-found" but returns empty
test reg --format 'SomeTag:%(tag("SomeTag")) SomeTagWithSpace:%(tag("Some Tag"))\n'
SomeTag:found SomeTagWithSpace:
SomeTag:found SomeTagWithSpace:
end test
